00:10:11,176 --> 00:10:13,439
好吧，拜伦小姐 你想采访吗？写下来
All right, Miss Bryant, do you want an interview? Write this down.

173
00:10:13,545 --> 00:10:14,499
你有没天真地想过…
Are you naive enough to think

174
